		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />- blargg MMC3 test ROMs
<br />- Incredible Crash Test Dummies
<br />- Crystalis
<br />- Kickmaster (titlescreen is tricky -- also poor emulation may cause it to crash after level 2)
<br />- Megman 3 (sort of -- try going in Gemini man's stage and bringing up the pause menu -- if you're doing things wrong it'll be screwed up)
<br />- Wolverine
<br />
<br />Those are all I can think of at the moment.

		

		</td>
